preference.name: TC__thumbnail_dataset_type_priority_order
preference.preference_description: Defines the order in which the datasets will be queried for the thumbnail image to display. Valid values are internal dataset type names. The first value in the list gets the highest priority and then progressively lower priority. The datasets order will first be evaluated by the order of the relation types defined in the "TC__thumbnail_relation_order" preference. The order sorting by the dataset type from this preference will happen after that.
